sbol:ComponentDefinition.addgene:growthInstructions: For production of astaxanthin, introduce this plasmid into E. coli strain TOP10 that already contains plasmid pAC-BETA or pAC-BETAipi, induce expression of the hbfd1 cDNA with arabinose (0.1% is satisfactory), and grow in liquid culture on a platform shaker at 28 degrees Celsius in darkness for 2-3 days.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.addgene:refMethod: pCBFD1/HBFD1Bad was a gift from Francis X Cunningham Jr (Addgene plasmid # 53364 ; http://n2t.net/addgene:53364 ; RRID:Addgene_53364)

sbol:ComponentDefinition.addgene:modificationsToBackbone: To make pCBFD1/HBFD1Bad, the cbfd1 cDNA was excised from pCBFD1 as a PvuII-XhoI fragment and ligated into pHBFD1Bad that had been digested with KpnI, blunted with the Klenow enzyme, purified by phenol/chloroform extraction, and then digested with XhoI and gel purified.
